# Engineering Guardrails

## Stack

- React + TypeScript
- Modern CSS + CSS variables
- Minimal dependencies

Code must be:
- readable
- predictable
- intentionally boring

---

## Do NOT Introduce

- theming systems
- heavy abstractions

## Accessibility (Non-Negotiable)

- Keyboard accessible interactions
- Visible focus states
- WCAG AA contrast
- Motion respectful
